Ok, i guess i should update, its been like weeks since i have because i kinda swore off of this thing, but whatever.  I can't sleep for some reason.  Every night for the past month i've been having trouble staying up and tonight i just don't want to go to sleep.  Oh well.  I'm so excited for the next two weeks:

Fri. May 13th-Prom
   we have a limo but no more hotel because it costs too much, instead, we're gonna just go to      afterparties and stuff till 5am

Sat May 14th
   Band Banquet, i hope everyone goes =\

Sun. May 15th
   My 8 month anniversary <3

Saturday May 21st
   Military Ball, and may i say, i am very excited b/c i bought the most GORGEOUS dress

Wed. May 25th
   Seniors' last day of school =( i'm probably gonna cry that day.

So there you have it. An update on my life for those of you who care.  I have so much on my mind right now but none of it is suitable for an online journal for everyone to see.  Nothing bad, just confusing.  Oh well, ::sigh::, i guess i'll go watch TV until i fall asleep. 

<3<3<3 Kris

omg spring break is off to such a friggin great start. our spring break trip was soooo much fun.  the 8 of us (me, boy, nic, samo, pooks, ed, sebass, and sexton) all went to universal for 3 days without any parents.  it was fun x's 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000.... u get my point.  we made so many amazingly fun memories together.  i can't wait to get the pictures back! =)

well that's it, i won't be online much this spring break b/c i plan on having a hell of a fun time. later.

<3 kris

omg i am so  s o r e.

 

someone please come to chop my legs off.

i had such a good day  yesterdat that it's worthy of an entry.  

i woke up at 8:00 and went to mcdonalds by 9:00, i got two free breakfast sandwiches ontop of the deluxe breakfast that i ordered, so i went to nellys to give them to her and cindy.  that intended 15 minute visit ended up being a visit from 9:00 am to almost 6:00 pm.  it was so much fun though.  we watched spanish porn(not really though) and hung out with a south american rich kid.  i have to visit nelly more often, so much fun and i brushed up on my spanish skills =\ 

then i went out to dinner with boy at tarpon bend.  it was fun, even though i had tomatoes in my chicken wrap.  we went back to his house for like 10 minutes and then i went to chili's to see nic and the ace people.  they're so much fun, i wish i had a job there.  from there me and nic went to the carnival and met up with snot kaitlin, pooks, bailey, ed, and later tyler.  we rode one ride like a million times b/c the carny liked us and then we rode  the ferris wheel.  it wasn't as bad this year (scary, i mean) because i got over my fear of ferris wheels last year when me, nic, fien, and chase rode it at the president's fest.  All three of them made me ride it last year and i was gripping onto that damn pole so hard.  Well, we got cotton candy and then i drove kaitlin and snot home and nicolette slept over.  fun times.  like i said, yesterday was SOO much fun! 

well, hope you liked my update. check for another one next month. lol.

<3, Kris

hmmm...i forgot what it's like to update in livejournal. its actually oddly exciting.  anyway, i'm having a good break, or at least until tonight.  i decided i would get started on the homework that my english and history teachers couldn't resist assigning,that is, until i looked for my history notebook and couldn't find my notebook.  i swear for the life of me that i put it in my guard bag and it stayed put until i got home from practice.  but, the next minute, my mom cleaned out my guard bag to take out the dirty clothes and my notebook is now suddenly  disappeared.  you probably don't care...alright...

anyhow, my break's been pretty good. i've spent a lot of time with boy and a lot of time with my family. i called yeff to hang out tonight but he never called me back. jerkface...

i still can't believe im updating.  

guard = pain in my ass (i can't wait to graduate) I go to check my email today for the first time this break, and (no disrespect to the email writers) my entire inbox was flooded with emails about more mandatory guard crap and reminders of the 8 hour practice i have breathing down my neck.  yuck.  

tomorrow's new year's eve, so like always, i'll spend it in miami somewhere with my big cuban family.  At least this year i'll have someone to kiss at midnight =)

Well, i <3 u all, and don't expect this updating nonsense to happen everyday.

Kris

School sucks so bad....homework is consuming my life entirely. oh well. more important issues....

Happy Birthday Fien! (I hope you had fun with liz, i just wish i couldve been part of you seventeenth birthday)

Today was nicolette and billy's 6 month.  =) @-,-----

Yo asses. wuddup. crazy weekend. too much practice. fuck friedman and his stupid practices.  no reason to practice. they just want us to die. akward entry, i know.  deal.  comment on how much you hate practice.

damn it, im dead if it hits us straight on.  ill take all my clothes and my dog and run into the closest house with shutters.  it seems so weird because everybodys going crazy, yet if you look outside, its a perfect day for the beach.  I hope all this hurricane bullshit is over by monday so i can go to the beach bitches.

i should be doing hw, but f that.  game on friday was fun, some shit was going on, but nonetheless it was fun. i had to pee sooo bad at the end though and i couldnt until i dropped nicolette off. then she threw ice at me. saturday at friday's was fun too. when the friday's opens up by muvico, i wanna get a job there.  anywho, i figured i'd update cuz i havent in two weeks, so this is my update.  peace out bitches.  <333

i dont even care that much, im just thinking about this to take my mind off of other things. but it would be nice if everyone commented to give me something else to think about.

also, who in guard wants to go bowling tomorrow night? i might go to the picnic and if i do go, ill bring it up then i guess.alright, im leaving to read my book for a.p. classes.

i can't even think about the other night without breaking into tears. i just wanna let fien and nic know that no matter what happened between us, you are the best and truest friends i have ever had and the only ones that really cared about me. i love you guys so much and if anything had ever happened to you that night, i would never be able to live with myself knowing that i let something so stupid come between us. I guess that's the reason why it hurts me so much to think about it. I will forever pray and thank God for watching over you that night. I will never be able to understand what you guys went through, but i can only imagine you will never forget it. I love you two so much and i will ALWAYS be here for you from here on out. <333 Kris

I've had the most eventful days of my summer in this last week. But i don't really feel like writing about it, and it doesnt make a difference if i wrote about it or not, i still wouldn't get any comments =(. whatever, anyhow, i've had alot of fun with the guard lately. i'm glad that i picked guard to do my freshman year because it's such a fun activity and you get to have like a second family...

me and mariela talked on the phone last night from 12 until 3 am. it was crazy. i dont even know what we talked about lol.  yesterday, me and michelle kept getting hit on by minorities hahahaha, dont ask.  it was scary though.  and then i got the HUGEST icecream cone at mcdonalds and headed over to mariela's house for like 10 minutes.  omg! nelly gets home today! omg i have to go call her, this update is now over lol.  <33333

i've been so damn lazy lately.  i havent called anybody to do anything just because i HATE HATE HATE  making plans.  So if anyone wants to hang out before summer's over, call me because i doubt i'll call you. (heh, i'm probably not gonna get any phone calls still, oh well)

 

another complaint, i need a job, but i dont know if i can handle one during marching season...?

 

i was watching surreal life on vh1 and i've now been motivated to make my year long goal "being yourself".  If i were trishelle, i would be an "alcoholic slut"-Sally Jesse Raphael.

 

<3 Kris

the notebook was the most amazing movie i have seen in the longest time. it is now and forever will be my favoritest movie. the only thing that sucked about it is that now im always going to be comparing every single guy to noah and will always be dissapointed because there is no noah in real life.  But i swear to you, if i ever meet a noah in my lifetime...marrying him. 

<333 kris

I went to the doctor today to see why the hell my shoulder is in so much pain and how to fix my deformed feet. I was there from 2:00 till 5:11. I wanted to kill myself towards the end because i was so hungry and bored and cold and tired. Anyhow, for my shoulder, i have to not use it at all, ice it, and take medication for a week. I asked if i could go to guard practice but the doctor said no.(which i hate because then all the other guard girls always think that im just trying to get out of practice or its not that serious or not really hurting that bad)whatever. For my feet, i have to wear some arch thing in my sneakers and get surgery on both my big toes, but one at a time, and the recovery will take 6 weeks, with me in a big boot ='( oh well.

 

I GOT BANGS!!!!!!!

how freaking cool is that? i love my bangs =)

 

Im going to canada in like 2 weeks to see my brother.  He says its nice in canada, like a clean new york.  whatever.

 

well im gonna stop writing now and figure out what im gonna do tonight. <3333

summer sucks! im so bored! nelly and yeff are gone, nelly for a month and yeff for a week.  bleh. please, hang out with me. 
<33333

i got back from vacation saturday. it was so much fun.  i wouldve had alot more fun if i could've invited another friend's family, but i still had fun with my brother, his girlfriend, and my mom's friend's daughter's who are my age.  (confused yet?) i really did have a great time and it was the first time in a while that ive gone away and not wished that i was at home.  the cruise was good to figure out my personality and who i liked, didn't like, got along with, couldnt live without, and all that mumbo jumbo.  i got a nice tan out of it all too 8D . went to practice today and missing a week sure screws you up.  oh well, ill make up for it in the next few weeks to come.  THERE'S ONLY A FEW MORE WEEKS OF SUMMER LEFT AND I HAVE TO READ FOUR BOOKS AND WRITE TWO ESSAYS!!!! side note-sorry to the people i didnt tell i was going away for a week.  i left my cellphone at home on the charger and i had 18 missed calls. oh well,  now you know.  i kind of wish i was back on the cruise again, it was all new people and a fresh place to start....whatever...im gonna go read or call somebody or something now.  update later.

<3333333

yo. my day wasnt anything special. actually, it was pretty down right shitty at one point because i overheard some people saying something not so nice about me. whatever, i'm way over it. but besides that, today was just a huge day of review for finals tomorrow and thursday. im SO happy that school's almost finally over! concussion last night was so crazy good! it wasnt as good as the first show, but it was still good enough that i stayed for the second show, didnt get home until 11 and am falling asleep all day today as a result. nadia and reva are so cool. nadia has hot short hair now and reva can read tarot cards which she better read them for me <U>SOON! </U>=)  well i gotta go review for my math final now. im out.  <333 kris

sorry to all of you that don't have a live journal and want to comment, just e-mail me from now on kris_7506@hotmail.com.  due to some unwanted technical difficulties, i had to block anonymous replies.  sorry again. =\

i am no longer a decent, normal person. i am a sick person who shouldn't be allowed near a computer. i realized how fun it is to be able to know about a person's life without them ever knowing it. omg, now im saying it's fun, I'VE GONE MAD! i've started on this new life, i just need it to be a little more complete. omg...im gonna go lay down or something because i am insane.

live journal is sick. i just spent valuable time reading some kid's lj that i dont even know, and im a somewhat normal, decent person. i dont wanna think about all the weird people that could be reading my lj. oh well. i guess if i dont htink about it then it doesnt matter. anyhow, in reading that person's lj, i realized that i want a bf. i think a bf would make my life complete right now. i know that a guy shouldnt be anybodys main focus in life or whatever, but my life is treating me so well lately. i have good friends, im hanging out with so many people i stopped hanging out with for a while, i have a great relationship with my parents, and my school work is finally looking up. and im finally happy!i just want a boy to be able to come to when im bored, or scared, or sad, or just want someone to hold. it sounds stupid, i know, but this is the way i feel. i just want someone to tell me that they love me and that im the world to them. well, now that ive poured out my naive(sp?) little heart, im gonna go do my homework for tomorrow. 6 more days of school!!! <3333

hey. its been a few days since ive updated.  well...my weekend wasnt anything special. on friday i saw new york minute with michelle.( i know, i know, im supporting those damn olsen twins)The movie wasn't actually half bad. My favorite part was seeing my beautiful future husband, riley smith. i swear, i am going to marry him. if you dont know who he is, watch motocross on the disney channel or hes the cute guy on the tv show raising dad.  the rest of the weekend went something like this: hair done, nails done, military ball, shitty time, drove around, mcdonalds, got grounded, little cousins party, hw.  and yesterdya i left school early because i was on the verge of puking my life out. and i stayed home today.  and im about to eat some food, so i have to leave now, because food is more important than anything in the world...well, not more important than riley smith.  
~Mrs. Riley Smith

Jeez does it suck to be sick...i stayed home today cuz in the morning, i had a low fever and i felt like shit.i dont think this semester ive been at school for a full week...not good, not good at all.  my teacher thinks im always skipping so my mom wrote her a nice little email making her feel bad ::evil grin:: anyhow, staring at the computer screen is making my head and eyes hurt...ill write more later when i feel better. 
oh, btw, i hope your pinky is recovering nice, nelly! =)

has anyone been on ratemyteachers.com? its awesome and a half.  i looked at all my teachers from cypress then i went to western and added chase to the list of teeachers and rated him "very easy" hahaha. i hope sam sees that and has a heart attack. i should have put a comment like "thanks for all the good times chaseyface".  (you cant put any bad words or profane things cuz they'll delete it when they screen it.) i miss chase so much.  i really need to see him soon or ill go nuts.  i have this huge math test tomorrow that i need to get an a on or else i have no chance of bringing my grade up in that class.  im so worried. i have a 72.5 in that classs (meanwhile others who are smart have 13%s and 25%s) and i wanna bring it up to a high b or even better an A.  yeah, i know its a long shot, but a girl can dream, cant she? wow im such a loser, im dreaming i get a's.  DAMN i need school to end.  well anyhow, i should go downstairs and help my mom entertain the family for mothers day. bye.
